data.description: Welcome to this exquisite 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home nestled in the highly sought-after Walnut Pass community. This stunning property offers a range of desirable features that are sure to captivate you! As you enter, you'll be greeted by a beautifully designed entry way and dining room that   provides a perfect space for entertaining guests and enjoying meals with family and friends, in addition to the inviting living room featuring a striking stone accent wall, setting the tone for the elegance that awaits.  The island kitchen is a chef's dream, boasting stainless steel appliances, 42-inch cabinets, gas cooking, granite countertops, and a stylish tile backsplash. With its ample space and convenient eat-in area, the kitchen is perfect for casual dining and culinary exploration. Upstairs, you'll find a loft area that can be utilized as a versatile space, accommodating your specific needs and generously sized bedrooms, ensuring comfort and privacy for everyone in the household. The primary bedroom is a true sanctuary, complete with a double vanity, a walk-in shower, a luxurious soaker tub, and a spacious walk-in closet. The secondary bathroom has been thoughtfully updated with a large walk-in shower, ensuring comfort and convenience for guests or family members. Step outside into your very own backyard oasis, where you'll discover a heated pool and hot tub, offering year-round relaxation and enjoyment. The covered patio provides a shaded retreat, while the beautifully landscaped backyard with trees offers privacy and tranquility. Additionally, a storage shed provides extra space for your belongings. One of the many advantages of this property is the absence of backyard neighbors, ensuring a peaceful and serene environment. Furthermore, this home is the ideal location for convenient living and access to a variety of amenities and entertainment options. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this exceptional property your new home!
